Befitting tops for Palazzo 
Embellished and stylish pants, without doubt, make great statement outfits, but considering the flared nature of palazzo pants, you would need to match with a perfect body-fitting top that is not conspicuously oversized. It could be spaghetti strap, off-shoulder, fitted round or V-neck top, crop tops, tank tops, lace tops, or even shirts, but whatever style of top you chose, ensure it is body-fitting. However, if your palazzo pants are made with printed fabric, ensure to pair with plain top, while your plain pants should be paired with a printed top. Best colours for Palazzos
